Know More about us

Brand Story

Our founder began his journey with only one intention - to always bring the best quality product for your everyday gadgets! He launched Kalakaar to serve the colourful taste of our vibrant country. With a vision to cater to individual tastes, Kalakaar only deals with premium materials like Silicone, glass, marble, and more and each product is crafted in-house to ensure that every product is the perfect match for your gadget. After making it big with Phone covers and cases, Kalakaar now offers a full range of products for everyday usage. From designer water bottles to Bluetooth speakers, and from air tags to watch straps, Kalakaar does it all!
